data.description: Start living in this fantastic 3-bedroom home featuring a spacious 2-car garage and RV gate/parking. The interior boasts plush carpeting, a neutral color scheme, and sleek tile floors. Relax in the cozy living room or entertain in the family room. The modern kitchen highlights espresso cabinets, glossy granite counters, stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. The main bedroom comes with a private bathroom for added comfort. Outside, enjoy a covered patio, separate laundry room, storage shed, rear vehicle entry, and ample space for a potential pool and gatherings. A must-see gem!
